#Title
Change device orientation on map page

#Description
On the map page of application change device orientation

#Pre-conditions
The application is installed

#Steps
1. Run the application
2. Wait until cities list is loaded
3. Scroll down to the 'Aalburg, NL' city
4. Click on 'Aalburg, NL'
5. Wait until map page is loaded
6. Change device orientation to landscape and back to portrait

#Expected result
Application is running
Map page shows city on the map